        &mt LGUI A  &mt LALT R  &mt LCTRL S  &mt LSHFT T  &kp G        &kp M          &mt RSHFT N  &mt RCTRL E  &mt RALT I  &mt RGUI O
&trans  &trans      &kp X       &kp C        &kp D        &kp V        &kp K          &kp H        &kp Q        &kp Z       &trans      &trans
                                &kp DEL      &lt 1 TAB    &kp SPACE    &kp BACKSPACE  &lt 2 ESC    &kp RET
